        <abstract> 
<p>Has finished last revise of his book [<hi rend="italic">Variation</hi>].</p> 
            <p>Is curious to know what JDH thinks of Pangenesis. It is fearfully imperfect, yet satisfying, for it connects large groups of facts by an intelligible thread.</p>
            <p>Thomas Woolner is coming [to do a bust of CD].</p>
        </abstract>
